{"tid":673799,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓威脅取消「特金會」，美國副總統Mike Pence：我哋特朗普都可能會唔去！","createTime":"2018-05-22T07:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T07:12:27.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64d851737bd5c09628be81df6bd75efc541a80eb","tid":673799,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"對於早前北韓威脅會考慮取消美朝首腦峰會，美國副總統彭斯(Mike Pence)警告，北韓最高領導人金正恩「咪玩嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯向霍士新聞台(Fox News)表示，北韓不應試圖以不打算遵守的承諾，來迫使美國讓步。他強調，若然金正恩認為自己可以把特朗普玩弄於股掌之間的話，那將是大錯特錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n被問到特朗普是否仍可能退出預定下月12日在新加坡召開的美朝首腦峰會時，彭斯回應稱，這是亳無疑問的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n另外，南韓總統文在寅今日訪美，將於當地時間中午與特朗普舉行首腦會談。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社早前引述消息指，鑑於美朝在無核化方法上存在矛盾，文在寅或會爭取在美國堅持的一步到位無核化，與朝方提出的分步同時無核化之間找到妥協點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1848405/%E5%BD%AD%E6%96%AF%3A%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E4%BB%8D%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E7%BE%8E%E6%9C%9D%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1848405%2F%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E6%2596%25AF%253A%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%259C%259D%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=l5eGLvVAMMxnCWCHCGEdVJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=e4f7c44e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1848405/%E5%BD%AD%E6%96%AF%3A%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E4%BB%8D%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E7%BE%8E%E6%9C%9D%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83</a>"},{"pid":"f8376684b1163e641aea668a03144c1892029ca3","tid":673799,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e90b292c4821c21d212e24a1ae3e8e11271fee9","tid":673799,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:12:27.000Z","msg":"又撚狗"}]}